Package com.neu.prattle.model

Class BasicGroup

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.neu.prattle.model.BasicGroup
  • @Entity
public class BasicGroup
extends java.lang.Object
    POJO for a Group of users. Could fairly easily be used instead of User. Has Builder and classically named getters/setters if we need a convenient way to create them from js.
